    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, sending power through a factory variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension geometry remains precise with recently refreshed bushings, offering exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. While the aesthetics reflect its well-maintained status with minor honest patina, the drivetrain is optimized for performance, delivering the visceral, analog feedback enthusiasts crave.",
      "price": 34500.0,
