      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery is supple with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all dashboard controls, including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has a documented service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last season. It drives straight, shifts smoothly through all gears, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, honest car that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and never smoked in.",
